lution for the given minimization\nproblem above. We demonstrate that strong convexity and $2-$convexity are\nactually different names for the same concept. In addition to these facts, we\nmake us of Bregman divergence in order to be able to quantify the rate of\nconvergence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Aug 2015 11:49:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 6 Sep 2015 12:06:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-08"}
